WEBVTT

00:03.000 --> 00:05.500
ALLISON:
<i>when I was?????
Mrs Water</i>

00:05.500 --> 00:07.400
 <i>she???? bring me
her daughter's old clothes.</i>

00:07.500 --> 00:09.300
 <i>I never wanted to wear them.</i>

00:10.200 --> 00:12.300
 <i>It wasn't that I didn't</i>
 <i>like the clothes,</i>

00:12.300 --> 00:15.300
 <i>it was the way they made me</i>
 <i>feel whenever I put them on.</i>

00:16.600 --> 00:18.450
 <i>Later, I found out that</i>

00:18.450 --> 00:20.850
 <i>when Mrs. Walters' little girl</i>
 <i>would misbehave,</i>

00:21.000 --> 00:23.967
 <i>she would lock her</i>
 <i>in a dark closet.</i>

00:27.650 --> 00:29.884
 <i>Then there was the time</i>
 <i>I was about to sit down</i>

00:29.917 --> 00:31.200
 <i>on the couch</i>
 <i>and watch television,</i>

00:31.500 --> 00:34.000
 <i>and suddenly, I got</i>
 <i>the distinct impression</i>

00:34.800 --> 00:38.800
 <i>that things between my mother</i>
 <i>and her latest boyfriend had...</i>

00:39.900 --> 00:41.700
 <i>moved to the next level.</i>

00:47.000 --> 00:50.200
 <i>My point being, that sometimes</i>
 <i>the energy from an event</i>

00:50.200 --> 00:52.100
 <i>can hang around</i>
 <i>a particular object</i>

00:52.100 --> 00:53.800
 <i>long after the event is over.</i>

00:54.600 --> 00:57.000
 <i>Almost like an imprint.</i>

00:57.300 --> 01:00.500
 <i>And people like me,</i>
 <i>people who are sensitive,</i>

01:01.600 --> 01:04.700
 <i>it's almost as if we can</i>
 <i>read the energy</i>

01:05.200 --> 01:06.400
 <i>and know what happened.</i>

01:08.000 --> 01:09.600
 <i>Like the time Bobby Page</i>

01:09.600 --> 01:11.800
 <i>taught me to shoot</i>
 <i>with his dad's rifle,</i>

01:13.800 --> 01:16.400
 <i>not knowing his dad had just</i>
 <i>used it to put down</i>

01:16.400 --> 01:18.300
 <i>their old retriever, Buck.</i>

01:20.200 --> 01:23.300
 <i>Yeah, that was</i>
 <i>a particularly bad energy.</i>

01:31.000 --> 01:33.500
 <i>And it isn't just the energy</i>
 <i>of other people's things,</i>

01:33.900 --> 01:35.700
 <i>other people's behavior,</i>

01:35.800 --> 01:37.800
 <i>that comes flooding</i>
 <i>back to me at times.</i>

01:43.633 --> 01:45.533
What? What?
What is it?

01:45.566 --> 01:47.500
 <i>The trick, I've learned,</i>
 <i>is to try to figure out</i>

01:47.500 --> 01:50.900
 <i>why the object is sharing</i>
 <i>that energy with you,</i>

01:51.000 --> 01:52.800
 <i>what the message might be,</i>

01:53.134 --> 01:58.900
 <i>and then, hopefully,</i>
 <i>behave accordingly.</i>

